<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200929/b801846535304cb2a2a9946857cbb893.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▲图片来自《iDest Magazine》</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">有点期待，她接下来又会在造型上，带给我们什么样的创新了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>——小S——</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200929/b1943c9d9c1d4fa1a0b03048a843961d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200929/ec26fddf5fc24195af4f742ba59cd9c0.png" max-width="600" /></p>
